{"tid":1798231,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"和你Shop, 幾個重點, 請注意","createTime":"2019-12-26T05:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T01:39:40.000Z","uid":76310,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a55c62b4daf7c85b46734bcb6db9b5e47779212f","tid":1798231,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:36:58.000Z","msg":"1. 唔洗裝修, 唔洗魔法, 唔洗玩具<br />\n商場, 就算全港最大既商場, 魔警包圍出口, 都好難走得甩<br />\n好多便衣狗在商場, 黑警在外包圍出口<br />\n仲有一大堆100%街坊樣既便衣狗睇水<br />\n所以唔好, 唔好, 唔好<br />\n<br />\n2.要100%街坊裝, 融入環境<br />\n有些額頭真係寫住&quot;我係手足&quot;<br />\n你要明白, 你是路過/你是去行街/你是去shopping<br />\n你雖然是林記, 都要專業, 例如:<br />\n女既化濃妝, 高跟鞋<br />\n街坊穿拖鞋<br />\n男既mk look/去玩look<br />\n<br />\n3.完成目標就走, 切忌戀戰, 切忌死磨<br />\n完成目標, 就要走, 不要留戀, 多一分鐘停留, 多一分危險<br />\n如落閘就閃<br />\n如大部份商戶關就閃,<br />\n如大部份顧客走, 就閃<br />\n<br />\n4.和你shop, 時間性要好<br />\n中午到晚上9時, 則最好, 因為多人<br />\n多: 港豬/離地撚/政治唔關我事/唔好煩到我/唔好煩到我, 先係最好和你Shop時間<br />\n唔好晚上好夜, 根本乜人都無<br />\n重點係多人質, 人質愈多愈好<br />\n<br />\n5. 靠把口足以影響他人行商場心情<br />\n例如叫口號, 用美心, 無良心<br />\n根本唔洗出手"},{"pid":"bc7199933220f5fcd1804635f7f8d1d148b92e6d","tid":1798231,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3043dccf2f752fed39b9f437aeb6cade4bf0c5c","tid":1798231,"uid":23239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:45:42.000Z","msg":"Push!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbd2efc9634ee984f1d2caf8bc8fba659de1e81","tid":1798231,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:49:48.000Z","msg":"記住重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\